Here you can see tools and ideas for getting access to the target machine, scanning port, networks, packages, info gathering 


1. whatweb IP-IP --aggression 3 -v --no-errors --log-verbose=results (scanning your network by internal IP using whatweb tool)

2. nmap <IP> (scanning all ports in the network using nmap tool)

3. reverseshell (hacking tool for getting remote access to the target machine)

4 .ssh (tool for getting remote access to the target)

5. gathering info tools (ping <IP or domain name>, nslookup <IP or domain name>)

6. arp -a utilizing this command you can check out all IPs of every device connected to your LAN 
